      "text": [
        "3990 - وَ رُوِيَ : \"أَنَّ حَدَّ اَلتَّلَقِّي رَوْحَةٌ فَإِذَا صَارَ إِلَى أَرْبَعِ فَرَاسِخَ فَهُوَ جَلْبٌ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3990 - It is narrated: \"The limit for intercepting is the distance of a short journey, but if it reaches four farsakhs, then it is considered transportation.\""
        ]
      }
    }
